sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as 用户
  participant FE as 前端页面<br/>ScriptEditor / VoiceGenerator / SegmentEditor
  participant Store as Zustand Store
  participant API as frontend services/api.ts
  participant BE as Express 后端
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant SSE as SSE 通道
  participant Queue as TTS 队列
  participant TTS as MiMo TTS API
  participant FS as backend/audio 文件系统

  U->>FE: 进入口播稿编辑页
  FE->>API: GET /api/voice-presets
  API->>BE: 获取已保存音色预设
  BE->>DB: SELECT voice_presets
  DB-->>BE: 预设列表，含 original_audio_path
  BE-->>API: presets
  API-->>Store: 写入 presets
  Store-->>FE: 渲染预设列表

  U->>FE: 选择一个“克隆”预设
  FE->>Store: updateVoiceConfig({ voiceType: clone, voiceClone: /audio/preset_original_x.wav })
  FE->>API: PATCH /api/broadcast/:id/voice-config
  API->>BE: 同步当前播报音色配置
  BE->>DB: UPDATE broadcasts.voice_type / voice_config
  DB-->>BE: OK
  BE-->>FE: broadcast

  opt 如果稿件还没切分
    U->>FE: 点击切分句子
    FE->>Store: splitScriptAction(text)
    Store->>API: POST /api/broadcast/generate<br/>mode=segmented + clone config
    API->>BE: 创建 segmented broadcast
    BE->>DB: INSERT broadcasts
    DB-->>BE: broadcast
    BE-->>Store: broadcast

    Store->>API: POST /api/broadcast/:id/split
    API->>BE: 请求切分
    BE->>DB: 读取 broadcast.content
    BE->>BE: mimo.splitScript(content)
    BE->>DB: INSERT segments
    BE->>FS: 清理旧整段音频
    BE->>DB: clearAudioAndSetMode(segmented)
    BE-->>Store: segments
    Store-->>FE: 渲染 SegmentEditor
  end

  FE->>SSE: GET /api/sse/:broadcastId
  SSE-->>FE: connected

  U->>FE: 点击“全部生成”
  FE->>Store: batchGenerateSegments(broadcastId)
  Store->>API: PATCH /api/broadcast/:id/voice-config
  API->>BE: 生成前再次同步当前 clone 配置
  BE->>DB: UPDATE broadcasts.voice_config
  BE-->>Store: OK

  Store->>API: POST /api/broadcast/:id/segments/batch-generate
  API->>BE: 批量生成 segment 音频
  BE->>DB: SELECT broadcast + pending/failed segments
  BE->>SSE: batch-generate-start

  loop 每个 pending/failed segment 串行处理
    BE->>DB: UPDATE segment.status = generating
    BE->>SSE: progress(generating)
    SSE-->>FE: 更新该句为“生成中”

    BE->>Queue: ttsQueue.enqueue()
    Queue->>FS: resolveVoiceClone(/audio/preset_original_x.wav)
    FS-->>Queue: 读取参考音频并转 base64/data URI
    Queue->>TTS: generateSpeech(text + clone voice data)
    TTS-->>Queue: audio buffer

    BE->>FS: 写入 segment_x_y.wav
    BE->>DB: UPDATE segment.status = generated, audio_path
    BE->>SSE: progress(generated, audioPath)
    SSE-->>FE: 更新该句为“就绪”并显示播放器
  end

  BE->>DB: SELECT 最新 segments
  BE->>SSE: complete(segments, results)
  SSE-->>FE: 替换完整 segments 状态
  BE-->>Store: HTTP 返回 segments/results

  U->>FE: 点击“合并音频”
  FE->>Store: mergeSegments(broadcastId)
  Store->>API: POST /api/broadcast/:id/segments/merge
  API->>BE: 请求合并
  BE->>DB: SELECT generated segments
  BE->>FS: 读取所有 segment wav
  BE->>BE: audio.mergeWavFiles()
  BE->>FS: 写入 broadcast_x_merged.wav
  BE->>DB: UPDATE broadcasts.audio_path/status
  BE-->>Store: broadcast
  Store-->>FE: 显示最终播放器
